5|$|The {{original}} scientific bureau, {{or think}} tank, of the Centre Democrats was the Stichting Wetenschappelijke Onderbouwing Centrumdemocratische Ideologie (Foundation for the Scientific Elaboration of the Centre Democratic Ideology, SWOCI). In 1992 its name {{was changed to}} the Thomas <b>Hobbes</b> Stichting (Thomas <b>Hobbes</b> Foundation), after Janmaat's favorite political philosopher.|$|E
5|$|In the 17th century, Leibniz, Thomas <b>Hobbes</b> and René Descartes {{explored}} {{the possibility that}} all rational thought could be made as systematic as algebra or geometry.|$|E
